@startuml
title TRIFORK-32 Quick Workflow

start
if (TRIFORK-32 already flashed?) then (yes)
else (no)
  :Run `cargo xtask flash`;
  :Press PROG on the board;
endif

:Edit `sw/program/src/main.rs`;
:Run `cargo xtask upload <COM_PORT>`;
:Build and upload program;
:TRIFORK-32 executes code;
:Observe UART output / LEDs;
stop
@enduml
